        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、标题"><a href="#一、标题" class="headerlink" title="一、标题"></a>一、标题</h2><p>为了使段落展示的更加清晰，Markdown中设置了多级标题的表达形式，级别用#来表示，几个#就表示几级标题，代码形式如下：</p><p>注意#后面要有一个空格</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 一级标题</span><br><span class="line">## 二级标题</span><br><span class="line">### 三级标题</span><br><span class="line">#### 四级标题</span><br><span class="line">##### 五级标题</span><br><span class="line">###### 六级标题</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>示例如下：</p><h2 id="一级标题"><a href="#一级标题" class="headerlink" title="一级标题"></a>一级标题</h2><h2 id="二级标题"><a href="#二级标题" class="headerlink" title="二级标题"></a>二级标题</h2><h3 id="三级标题"><a href="#三级标题" class="headerlink" title="三级标题"></a>三级标题</h3><h4 id="四级标题"><a href="#四级标题" class="headerlink" title="四级标题"></a>四级标题</h4><h5 id="五级标题"><a href="#五级标题" class="headerlink" title="五级标题"></a>五级标题</h5><h6 id="六级标题"><a href="#六级标题" class="headerlink" title="六级标题"></a>六级标题</h6><hr><h2 id="二、字体"><a href="#二、字体" class="headerlink" title="二、字体"></a>二、字体</h2><p>Markdown中提供了如下几种常用的字体格式。</p><p><strong>斜体</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*斜体*</span><br><span class="line">_斜体_</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>斜体</em><br><em>斜体</em></p><hr><p><strong>粗体</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">**粗体**</span><br><span class="line">__粗体__</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>粗体</strong><br><strong>粗体</strong></p><hr><p><strong>粗斜体</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">***粗斜体***</span><br><span class="line">___粗斜体___</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>粗斜体</strong></em><br><em><strong>粗斜体</strong></em></p><hr><p><strong>删除线</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~删除线~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><del>删除线</del></p><hr><p><strong>分割线</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">***</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p><strong>脚注</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是[^脚注]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这是[^脚注]</p><hr><p><strong>字体样式</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;font face=&quot;微软雅黑&quot; &gt;微软雅黑字体&lt;/font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot; &gt;宋体&lt;/font&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><font face="微软雅黑" >微软雅黑字体</font><br><font face="宋体" >宋体</font></p><hr><p><strong>字号</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;font size=3 &gt;3号字&lt;/font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;font size=4 &gt;4号字&lt;/font&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><font size=3 >3号字</font><br><font size=4 >4号字</font></p><hr><p><strong>颜色</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;font color=#FF0000 &gt;红色&lt;/font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;font color=#008000 &gt;绿色&lt;/font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;font color=#0000FF &gt;蓝色&lt;/font&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><font color=#FF0000 >红色</font><br><font color=#008000 >绿色</font><br><font color=#0000FF >蓝色</font></p><hr><p><strong>组合使用</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;font color=&quot;red&quot; face=&quot;黑体&quot; size=5&gt;hello world！&lt;/font&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><font color="red" face="黑体" size=5>hello world！</font></p><hr><p><strong>文本高亮显示</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;mark&gt;高亮显示&lt;/mark&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><mark>高亮显示</mark></p><hr><p><strong>添加背景颜色</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td bgcolor=&quot;yellow&quot;&gt;搞点颜色&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><tr><td bgcolor="yellow">搞点颜色</td></tr></table><hr><p><strong>文本注音</strong></p><blockquote><p>当我们遇到生僻字或者为了突出某个字的时候可以使用注音的方式。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;ruby&gt;饕餮 &lt;rt&gt;tāo tiè&lt;/rt&gt;&lt;/ruby&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><ruby>饕餮 <rt>tāo tiè</rt></ruby></p><hr><p><strong>下划线</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;u&gt;下划线&lt;/u&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><u>下划线</u></p><hr><h2 id="三、列表和板块"><a href="#三、列表和板块" class="headerlink" title="三、列表和板块"></a>三、列表和板块</h2><p>为了使得排版更清晰，Markdown中提供了多种格式的列表和排版块供我们组合使用。</p><p><strong>无序列表</strong></p><p>注意符号后面要有一个空格</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- 无序列表</span><br><span class="line">* 无序列表</span><br><span class="line">+ 无序列表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>无序列表</li></ul><ul><li>无序列表</li></ul><ul><li>无序列表</li></ul><hr><p><strong>有序列表</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. 第一项</span><br><span class="line">2. 第二项</span><br><span class="line">3. 第三项</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>第一项</li><li>第二项</li><li>第三项</li></ol><hr><p><strong>嵌套列表</strong></p><blockquote><p>使用嵌套列表的时候需要在子列表的前面加上4个空格。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- 第一级- 第二级</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>第一级<ul><li>第二级</li></ul></li></ul><hr><p><strong>区块引用</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; 外层区块</span><br><span class="line">&gt; &gt; 第一层区块</span><br><span class="line">&gt; &gt; &gt; 第二层区块</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>外层区块</p><blockquote><p>第一层区块</p><blockquote><p>第二层区块</p></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><hr><p><strong>片段代码块</strong></p><blockquote><p>Markdown中提供了能够随时在文本中添加片段代码块的方法。字符为键盘左上角的按键&#96;。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">`hello World`</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>hello World</code></p><hr><p><strong>代码块</strong></p><blockquote><p>Markdown中的代码块可以匹配几乎类型的代码样式。在使用的时候我们可以选择指定（也可不指定）对应的语言。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">```python</span><br><span class="line">print(&#x27;Hello World&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">```</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;Hello World&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p><strong>公式块</strong></p><blockquote><p>对于数学相关学者来说，通常需要编写数学公式，在Markdown可以使用$$来作为公式块，在其中进行Latex类型公式的输入。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$\sqrt&#123;2&#125; \quad and \quad \sqrt[n]&#123;3&#125;$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$\sqrt{2} \quad and \quad \sqrt[n]{3}$$</p><hr><h2 id="四、图片、链接与表格"><a href="#四、图片、链接与表格" class="headerlink" title="四、图片、链接与表格"></a>四、图片、链接与表格</h2><h3 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h3><p>Markdown在提供了控制图片添加大小、位置的方法。</p><p><strong>MD添加图片（传统方式）</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![图片描述](图片地址)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>使用img添加图片</strong></p><blockquote><p>使用img添加图片的时候，width用于控制宽度，height用于控制高度，div align用于控制位置（left、center、right）</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.baidu.com.1.png&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; height=&quot;192&quot; div align=center&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://baiyu1.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/012e3b5954ee3da8012193a387c830.png%401280w_1l_2o_100sh.png" alt="img"></p><hr><h3 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[百度](www.baidu.com)</span><br><span class="line">&lt;www.baidu.com&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="www.baidu.com">百度</a><br>&lt;<a href="http://www.baidu.com>">www.baidu.com&gt;</a></p><hr><h3 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h3><p><strong>添加表格</strong></p><blockquote><p>MD中添加表格的方式比较单一，添加表格的时候可以控制文字的对齐方式：</p><ul><li><strong>-:</strong> 设置内容和标题栏居右对齐。</li><li><strong>:-</strong> 设置内容和标题栏居左对齐。</li><li><strong>:-:</strong> 设置内容和标题栏居中对齐。</li></ul></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| 左对齐 | 右对齐 | 居中对齐 |</span><br><span class="line">| :-----| ----: | :----: |</span><br><span class="line">| 单元格 | 单元格 | 单元格 |</span><br><span class="line">| 单元格 | 单元格 | 单元格 |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="left">左对齐</th><th align="right">右对齐</th><th align="center">居中对齐</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">单元格</td><td align="right">单元格</td><td align="center">单元格</td></tr><tr><td align="left">单元格</td><td align="right">单元格</td><td align="center">单元格</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><p><strong>添加链接</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是博客主页： [YanTalk](https://yantalk.github.io/)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这是博客主页：<a href="https://yantalk.github.io/">YanTalk</a></p><hr><h2 id="五、流程图"><a href="#五、流程图" class="headerlink" title="五、流程图"></a>五、流程图</h2><p>很多人觉得Markdown的缺点就在于无法绘图，其实我们可以使用多种代码的组合进行多个流程图的绘制，示例如下：</p><p><strong>横向流程图</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">```mermaid</span><br><span class="line">graph LR</span><br><span class="line">A[方形] --&gt;B(圆角)</span><br><span class="line">B --&gt; C&#123;条件a&#125;</span><br><span class="line">C --&gt;|a=1| D[结果1]</span><br><span class="line">C --&gt;|a=2| E[结果2]</span><br><span class="line">F[横向流程图]</span><br><span class="line">```</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">graph LR</span><br><span class="line">A[方形] --&gt;B(圆角)</span><br><span class="line">B --&gt; C&#123;条件a&#125;</span><br><span class="line">C --&gt;|a=1| D[结果1]</span><br><span class="line">C --&gt;|a=2| E[结果2]</span><br><span class="line">F[横向流程图]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>纵向流程图</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">```mermaid</span><br><span class="line">graph TD</span><br><span class="line">A[方形] --&gt; B(圆角)</span><br><span class="line">B --&gt; C&#123;条件a&#125;</span><br><span class="line">C --&gt; |a=1| D[结果1]</span><br><span class="line">C --&gt; |a=2| E[结果2]</span><br><span class="line">F[竖向流程图]</span><br><span class="line">```</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">graph TD</span><br><span class="line">A[方形] --&gt; B(圆角)</span><br><span class="line">B --&gt; C&#123;条件a&#125;</span><br><span class="line">C --&gt; |a=1| D[结果1]</span><br><span class="line">C --&gt; |a=2| E[结果2]</span><br><span class="line">F[竖向流程图]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>纵向标准流程图</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">```mermaid</span><br><span class="line">flowchat</span><br><span class="line">st=&gt;start: 开始框</span><br><span class="line">op=&gt;operation: 处理框</span><br><span class="line">cond=&gt;condition: 判断框(是或否?)</span><br><span class="line">sub1=&gt;subroutine: 子流程</span><br><span class="line">io=&gt;inputoutput: 输入输出框</span><br><span class="line">e=&gt;end: 结束框</span><br><span class="line">st-&gt;op-&gt;cond</span><br><span class="line">cond(yes)-&gt;io-&gt;e</span><br><span class="line">cond(no)-&gt;sub1(right)-&gt;op</span><br><span class="line">```</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">flowchat</span><br><span class="line">st=&gt;start: 开始框</span><br><span class="line">op=&gt;operation: 处理框</span><br><span class="line">cond=&gt;condition: 判断框(是或否?)</span><br><span class="line">sub1=&gt;subroutine: 子流程</span><br><span class="line">io=&gt;inputoutput: 输入输出框</span><br><span class="line">e=&gt;end: 结束框</span><br><span class="line">st-&gt;op-&gt;cond</span><br><span class="line">cond(yes)-&gt;io-&gt;e</span><br><span class="line">cond(no)-&gt;sub1(right)-&gt;op</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>横向标准流程图</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br